      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">⚡</div>
        <div>
          <div class="feat-title">No Quality Loss</div>
          <div class="feat-desc">The original video content is not re-encoded aggressively — maximum quality is preserved.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">📱</div>
        <div>
          <div class="feat-title">Platform Ready</div>
          <div class="feat-desc">Output is optimized for TikTok, Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts, and other portrait-first platforms.</div>
        </div>
